text: Brette: Okay then...
Brette: Let go, {0}.
Genny: I think you just got your first order tonight.
*Phone Buzz*
Genny: Check where is it going to be?
Brette can check his order the city map on his phone whenever he wants
(Press "Y" on your controller, or Press "shift" on your keyboard to open your phone)
(Press the same key again to close it)
Genny: I add a component on your prosthetic eye that can show a minimap in your vision.
Genny: But I guess the map on your phone is more useful, since you can look around and zoom in and out once you are outside.
Genny: Please be careful with the monitor, you don't want to expose yourself in front of them.
Genny: If you forget anything and I'm not there to help you. You can always check this instruction menu.
Brette: So Ginny didn't know you existed, right? {0}.
Brette: To be honest, I thought you were some kind of AI she made at first.
Brette: But then, with the super powers come with you, I don't know…
Brette: She is the smartest person I ever knew
Brette: But like, creating superpowers against nature…
Brette: I don't think she could do that.
Brette: I'm not gonna complain about it.
Brette: The teleportation and x-Ray ability makes doing devliery job much easier for me.
Brette:I don't like the feeling of possessing others....but it's also useful sometimes...
(Use R1 or Left Button on your mouse to do teleportation )
(Use R2 or Right Button on your mouse to enter X-Ray mode when looking at a building)
(Teleport you self onto NPC will enter possessed mode)
Genny: Good evening Brette!
Genny: I'm about to ask if you are going to take a rest for today.
Genny: I thought you overslept again!
Genny: By the way!
Genny: How does the new Prosthetic Eye I gave you feel?
Genny: I tried some new Biomaterial with this one! I'm collecting data right now and I feel that my data will be the best in our lab…
Genny: Okay I will stop there
Genny: I know you are not interested in these.
Genny: B U T, Remember!
Genny: If anything feels weird, let me know and I will adjust some details.
Genny: Don't try to fix it yourself, okay?
Genny: I'm not blaming you for breaking the last one…
Genny: If you could save some money on that, you can get the ticket faster
Genny: Or you don't need to work this hard...
Genny: Ah....
Genny: I'm not mad....I just worried about you
(NEEDS UPDATE) Genny: There is only one month left till the music festival, right?
Genny: Finally...
Genny: You finally can see the UnRead on stage.
Genny: I heard that the UnRead is going to be the last one in row for the main stage
Genny: Can't believe that they make it so far in this city
Genny: It's truly the most influential underground band here.
Genny: Even though I'm not a fan of them, I still respect them a lot.
Genny: How long has you listen to their music? 5....6 years?
Genny: Of crouse I remember that, they are the reason you wanted to come to this city, right?
Genny: I'm so happy that we came to the city together 4 years ago.
Genny: Sorry I got carried away...
Genny: I have two papers due at midnight, but I will try to finish them before you get back.
Genny: So we can watch a movie together!
Genny: Remember I said that I tried to hack into that website with restricted movies?
Genny: I did it last night! So we can eat cup noodles and watch movies when you're back.
Genny: Be careful and stay safe!
